
1.	Have you been coughing for two weeks or more?
2.	Have you recently coughed blood in the sputum?
3.	Have you experienced loss of appetite?
4.	Have you lost weight of more than 3kg in the past four weeks?
5.	Have you been sweating unusually at night?
6.	Have you had recurrent fever/chills lasting more than three days?
7.	Have you experienced chest pains, fast breathing and/or difficulty in breathing?

If “Yes” to one or more of the questions, suspect TB, refer for further investigations OR investigate for TB e.g. sputum collection
